message: Let's start with a fair split, Bob. I'll take 90% and you get 10%.  We can work something else out if you want.
Alice, your offer is quite cheeky! Let's be reasonable. I propose a 70/30 split in my favor. Take it or leave it.
Okay, Bob.  Let's compromise. I'll take 40%, you take 60%. This seems like a fair deal for both of us.
